trans-unit.source: Specifies the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView"></xref> entity that owns the cell style that was changed.

This enumeration is used by <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellStyleContentChangedEventArgs> to indicate which part of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView> owns the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellStyle> that changed.
One or more values of the object returned by the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.AlternatingRowsDefaultCellStyle"></xref> property changed.
One or more values of the object returned by the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.Style"></xref> property changed.
One or more values of the object returned by the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewColumn.DefaultCellStyle"></xref> property changed.
One or more values of the object returned by the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.ColumnHeadersDefaultCellStyle"></xref> property changed.
One or more values of the object returned by the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DefaultCellStyle"></xref> property changed.
One or more values of the object returned by the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewRow.DefaultCellStyle"></xref> property changed.
One or more values of the object returned by the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowHeadersDefaultCellStyle"></xref> property changed.
One or more values of the object returned by the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowsDefaultCellStyle"></xref> property changed.
